Japanese:
格納庫から出ろ！
/c5※十字ボタンで歩く/c3
English:
Leave the hangar!
/c5* Walk with the D-Pad./c3

Japanese:
鉄クズを黄色い枠内に運べ！
/c5※腕がふれると鉄クズを持つ/c3
English: Carry the scraps of iron into the yellow zone! /c5* Touch the arms to the scrap iron to carry it./c3

Japanese:
手負いのオートマンを倒せ！
/c5※コクピットの左側の部分を叩き
　秘密のボタンを出現させろ/c3
English: Defeat the damaged Automan! /c5* Hit the left side of the control panel to make secret buttons appear./c3

Japanese:
すべての岩を黄色い枠内に運べ！
/c5※腕がふれると岩を持つ
　板から指を離すと岩を置く/c3
English: Carry all the rocks into the yellow zone! /c5* Touch rocks to grab them. Release the board to drop them./c3

Japanese:
手負いのオートマンを倒せ！
/c5※左上の歯車を回すと剣を振る
　限界以上回すと歯車は壊れる/c3
English: Defeat the damaged Automan! /c5* Turn the top-left gear to swing the sword. Excessive turning will break it./c3

Japanese:
制限時間内に、すべての鉄クズを
黄色い枠内に運べ！
English: Carry all the scrap iron into the yellow zone within the time limit!

Japanese:
制限時間内に線路上の岩を
すべて撤去、または破壊せよ！
/c5※駅を破壊すると作戦失敗/c3
English: Remove or destroy all the rocks on the track! /c5* If the station gets destroyed, you fail the mission./c3

Japanese:
制限時間内に黄色い枠内のビルを
すべて撤去、または破壊せよ！
English: Remove or destroy all buildings in the yellow zone within the time limit!

Japanese:
２体のオートマンを倒せ！
/c5※輸送車が破壊されると作戦失敗/c3
English:
Defeat the two Automen!
/c5* If the transport truck gets destroyed, you fail the mission./c3

Japanese:
相手より多くポールを破壊せよ！
/c5※破壊数は右上に白い数字で表示
　相手の破壊数は黄色で表示/c3
English: Destroy more poles than your opponent! /c5* You and your opponent's scores are shown on the upper right./c3

Japanese:
レースでアンマリーに勝利せよ！
/c5※サッカー場を右回りに１周して
　埠頭まで先に戻れば勝ち/c3
English:
Win the race against Anne-Marie!
/c5* Win by making a clockwise lap around the field, back to the wharf./c3

Japanese:
回転砲を搭載した
新型オートマンを倒せ！
English: Defeat the new Automan model, which is equipped with rotary cannons!

Japanese:
すべての敵とコントロール装置を
破壊せよ！　/c5※コントロール装置
がある限り、次々と敵が出現する/c3
English: Destroy all enemies and control devices! /c5* While control devices remain, enemies will keep appearing./c3

Japanese:
すべての敵とコントロール装置を
破壊せよ！　/c5※コントロール装置
がある限り、次々と敵が出現する/c3
English: Destroy all enemies and control devices! /c5* While control devices remain, enemies will keep appearing./c3

Japanese:
制限時間内に、爆弾をランバート
の店（黄色い枠内）まで運べ！
/c5※爆弾は強い衝撃を与えると爆発/c3
English: Carry the bomb to Lambert's shop (yellow zone)! /c5* A strong impact will set the bomb off./c3

Japanese:
アンマリーと力を合わせて
すべての敵を倒せ！
English: Together with Anne-Marie, defeat all enemies!

Japanese:
アンマリーと力を合わせて
敵を倒せ！
English: Together with Anne-Marie, defeat the enemy!

Japanese:
エリーと力を合わせて
すべての敵を倒せ！
English: Together with Ellie, defeat all enemies!

Japanese:
アンマリーと力を合わせて
人形王を倒せ！
English: Together with Anne-Marie, defeat the Mech King!

Japanese:
制限時間内に、すべての
トーテムを破壊せよ！
/c5※車での体当たりが有効/c3
English: Destroy all the totems within the time limit! /c5* Hitting them with your car will do the job./c3

Japanese:
制限時間内にすべてのトーテムを
破壊せよ！　/c5※相手より多くのト
ーテムを破壊しなければならない/c3
English: Destroy all the totems within the time limit! /c5* You must destroy more totems than your opponent./c3

Japanese:
制限時間内にすべてのトーテムを
破壊せよ！　/c5※相手より多くのト
ーテムを破壊しなければならない/c3
English: Destroy all the totems within the time limit! /c5* You must destroy more totems than your opponent./c3

Japanese:
敵をガケの下に落とせ！
/c5※自分がガケ下に落ちると
　作戦失敗/c3
English:
Knock the enemy off the cliff!
/c5* If you fall off the battlefield, you fail the mission./c3

Japanese:
仲間と力を合わせ、
すべての敵を倒せ！
English: Together with your partner, defeat all enemies!

Japanese:
敵を倒せ！
/c5※オメガカーゴが破壊
　されると作戦失敗/c3
English:
Defeat the enemy!
/c5* If the Omega Cargo gets destroyed, you fail the mission./c3

Japanese:
仲間と力を合わせ、
すべての敵を倒せ！
English: Together with your partner, defeat all enemies!

Japanese:
すべての敵を倒せ！
/c5※アンマリーが倒さ
　れると作戦失敗/c3
English:
Defeat all enemies!
/c5* If Anne-Marie is felled, you fail the mission./c3

Japanese:
喫茶店を駅の近くまで運べ！
/c5※開始直後、左側にある
　青い屋根の家が喫茶店/c3
English: Carry the cafe to the station! /c5* From the start, the blue-roofed house on the left is the cafe./c3

Japanese:
レースでエリーに勝利せよ！
/c5※矢印の通りにコースを進み
　先に二周すれば勝ち/c3
English: Win the race against Ellie! /c5* Follow the course shown by the arrows. If you lead after two laps, you win./c3

Japanese:
レースでリューに勝利せよ！
/c5※矢印の通りにコースを進み
　先に二周すれば勝ち/c3
English: Win the race against Ryuu! /c5* Follow the course shown by the arrows. If you lead after two laps, you win./c3

Japanese:
レースで勝利せよ！
/c5※矢印の通りにコースを進み
　先にゴールすれば勝ち！/c3
English: Win the race! /c5* Follow the course shown by the arrows. If you reach the goal first, you win!/c3

Japanese:
制限時間内にすべてのトーテムを
破壊せよ！　/c5※相手より多くのト
ーテムを破壊しなければならない/c3
English: Destroy all the totems within the time limit! /c5* You must destroy more totems than your opponent./c3

Japanese:
レースで勝利せよ！
/c5※矢印の通りにコースを進み
　先に三周すれば勝ち/c3
English: Win the race! /c5* Follow the course shown by the arrows. If you lead after three laps, you win./c3

Japanese:
レースで勝利せよ！
/c5※矢印の通りにコースを進み
　先に二周すれば勝ち/c3
English: Win the race! /c5* Follow the course shown by the arrows. If you lead after two laps, you win./c3

Japanese:
輸送車を黄色い枠内に誘導せよ！
/c5※近づくと、輸送車はこちらに
　よって来る/c3
English: Lead the transport truck into the yellow zone! /c5* The truck will follow you when you get close to it./c3

Japanese:
制限時間以内に、指定された数
の石像を黄色い枠内に運べ！
/c5※石像の数は右上に表示/c3
English: Carry the statues into the yellow zone within the time limit! /c5* The statue count is on the upper right./c3

Japanese:
制限時間内に、すべての金塊を
駅（黄色い枠内）まで運べ！
English: Carry all the stacks of gold to the station (yellow zone) within the time limit!

Japanese:
すべてのコマンドティーガーを
倒せ！

すべてのコマンドティーガーを
倒せ！
すべてのオートマンを倒せ！

ゴリラと力を合わせ
すべての敵を倒せ！
English: Together with the gorilla, defeat all enemies!

Japanese:
制限時間内に、輸送車を黄色い枠
内に運べ！
/c5※輸送車が破壊されると作戦失敗/c3
English: Carry the transport truck into the yellow zone! /c5* If the truck gets destroyed, you fail the mission./c3

Japanese:
敵の車をすべて破壊せよ！
/c5※車での体当たりが有効/c3
English: Destroy all the enemy cars! /c5* Hitting them with your car will do the job./c3

Japanese:
リューと力を合わせ
すべての敵を倒せ！
English: Together with Ryuu, defeat all enemies!

Japanese:
すべてのコマンドティーガーを
倒せ！
/c5※忍工房が破壊されると作戦失敗/c3
English: Defeat all the Commando Tigers! /c5* If the Shinobi Workshop gets destroyed, you fail the mission./c3

Japanese:
すべてのコマンドティーガーを
倒せ！
/c5※神社が破壊されると作戦失敗/c3
English:
Defeat all the Commando Tigers! /c5* If
the shrine gets destroyed, you fail the mission./c3

Japanese:
アンマリーと協力し
すべての敵を倒せ！
English: Cooperate with Anne-Marie to defeat all enemies!

Japanese:
エリーと協力し、
すべての敵を倒せ！
English: Cooperate with Ellie to defeat all enemies!

Japanese:
リューと協力し、
すべての敵を倒せ！
English: Cooperate with Ryuu to defeat all enemies!

Japanese:
アインと協力し、
すべての敵を倒せ！
English: Cooperate with Ein to defeat all enemies!

Japanese:
新型オートマンをすべて倒せ！
/c5※しばらく持ちこたえれば
/c5　アンマリーが応援にくる/c3
English:
Defeat all the new-model Automen!
/c5* If you can hang on for a bit, Anne-Marie will come to your aid./c3

Japanese:
ザ・バーガーの店舗（赤い屋根の
店）二つを破壊または線路の向こ
う側へ撤去し、敵を全滅せよ！
English: Destroy or relocate the two {The Burger} shops (the red-roofed stores), on the other side of the railway, and defeat the enemy!

Japanese:
仲間と力を合わせ、
すべての敵を倒せ！
English: Together with your partner, defeat all enemies!

Japanese:
黄色い枠内のすべての建物と歩道
橋（喫茶店を除く）を撤去せよ！
/c5※喫茶店を破壊すると作戦失敗/c3
English: Remove everything (except the cafe) from the yellow zone! /c5* Destroy the store, and you fail the mission./c3

Japanese:
レースで勝利せよ！
/c5※誰よりも速くサーキットを
　三周すれば勝ち/c3
English:
Win the race!
/c5* Complete three laps before anyone else to win./c3

Japanese:
レースで勝利せよ！
/c5※矢印の通りにコースを進み、
　先に二周すれば勝ち/c3
English: Win the race! /c5* Follow the course shown by the arrows, and win by leading after two laps./c3

Japanese:
レースで勝利せよ！
/c5※誰よりも速くサーキットを
　五周すれば勝ち/c3
English: Win the race! /c5* Complete five laps before anyone else to win./c3

Japanese:
マリオネットビーと力を合わせ
すべての敵を倒せ！
English: Together with the Marionette Bees, defeat all enemies!

Japanese: マリオネーションキラーを倒せ！

アンマリーと協力し、すべての
マリオネーションキラーを倒せ！
English: Cooperate with Anne-Marie to defeat all the Marionation Killers!

Japanese:
次々あらわれるマリオネーション
キラーをすべて倒せ！　/c5※強力な
人形がなければ、勝利は難しい/c3
English: Defeat the onslaught of Marionation Killers! /c5* Without a powerful mech, victory will be difficult./c3

Japanese:
敵をすべて倒し、エリーを救え！
/c5※エリーがやられると作戦失敗/c3
English:
Defeat all enemies and save Ellie!
/c5* If Ellie goes down, you fail the mission./c3

Japanese:
すべての敵を倒して八工房会議を
守れ！　/c5※コマンドティーガーが
破壊されると作戦失敗/c3
English: Defeat all enemies and defend the Conference! /c5* If the Commando Tiger gets destroyed, you fail the mission./c3

Japanese:
輸送車を救出し、黄色い枠内まで
運べ！
/c5※輸送車が破壊されると作戦失敗/c3
English: Rescue the transport truck and carry it to the yellow zone! /c5* If the truck gets destroyed, you fail the mission./c3

Japanese:
アンマリーと力を合わせ
すべての敵を倒せ！
English: Together with Anne-Marie, defeat all enemies!

Japanese:
アンマリーと力を合わせ
二体の人形王を倒せ！
English: Together with Anne-Marie, defeat the two Mech Kings!

Japanese:
ファウストと力を合わせ
すべての敵を倒せ！
English: Together with Faust, defeat all enemies!
